}

try, catch, finally:

Operators:
$i++;
++$j;

Casting:
$intValue = (int) $input;

Binary opeators:
if ($a === $b) {
    $foo = $bar ?? $a ?? $b;
} elseif ($a > $b) {
    $foo = $a + $b * $c;
}

Ternary operator:
$variable = $foo ? 'foo' : 'bar';
